<i>Happy birthday, dear Daaaan.</i>

90
00:07:34,270 --> 00:07:38,800
<i>Happy birthday to you.</i>

91
00:07:38,820 --> 00:07:41,860
- Ha, ha, ha, ha!
- Ha, ha, ha, ha!

92
00:07:41,990 --> 00:07:44,290
- Quẩy phát không!
- Ừ! Lên! Quẩy lên!

93
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:48,180
Quẩy lên bà con ơi!

